results.name: E.g.f. satisfies: A(x) = x*exp( A(x)/A'(x) ).
link: Vaclav Kotesovec, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..250
formula: (1) A(x)/A'(x) = -G(-x) where G(x) = x + x*G(x)*G'(x) is a g.f. of A088716; thus, log(A(x)/x) is an integer series.
(2) A(-L(-x)) = x where L(x) = x*exp(x*L'(x)) is the e.g.f. of A161968.
